oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Dorothy Gracy, daughter of one of the college professors, spills Sopjes in jiu-jitsu demonstration
oai_dc:dc.dc:rights: For current rights information, please visit: http://idserver.utk.edu/?id=200600000001200
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Dorothy Gracy, daughter of a Middle Tennessee State College professor, flips Sopjes in a jiu-jitsu demonstration. During a homefront war bond rally on the Murfreesboro public square, the College Training Detachment hosted demonstrations and speeches for the entertainment of the assembled crowd.
The University of Tennessee Libraries (Knoxville, Tennessee) is the digital publisher.
